A LyX port of André Miede's Classic Thesis template

Original by Nick Mariette, March 2009.
Reworked for v3.0 by Ivo Pletikosić, May 2011.
Updates to later versions by Ivo Pletikosić
Latest update as of June 2018


To open ClassicThesis.lyx and accompanying files, make sure you have
LyX version 2.3+





